applications

类 FloatingApplication

  • java.lang.Object
    • core.Application
      • applications.FloatingApplication

  • public class FloatingApplication
extends Application
    Simple floating application to demonstrate the application support. The application can be configured to send floatings with a fixed interval or to only answer to floatings it receives. When the application receives a floating it sends a pong message in response. The corresponding FloatingAppReporter class can be used to record information about the application behavior.
    另请参阅:
    FloatingAppReporter

      • handle

        public Message handle(Message msg,
             DTNHost host)
        Handles an incoming message. Nothing done in this basic case where messages are only posted, but not replied to. This may serve as a hook to create more complex application logic.
        指定者:
        handle 在类中 Application
        参数:
        msg - message received by the router
        host - host to which the application instance is attached
        返回:
        the (possibly modified) message to forward or null if the application wants the router to stop forwarding the message.
